Fluent UI Emoji (raster pack)
=============================

The files under ``png/`` and ``manifest.json`` are produced by
``scripts/vendor_fluent_emoji.py`` from a clone of:

  https://github.com/microsoft/fluentui-emoji

See ``LICENSE-FLUENT-EMOJI`` in this directory and the upstream ``LICENSE`` in
that repository (MIT).

To refresh PNGs after changing ``EMOJI_CHARS``, from the repo root::

  python3 scripts/vendor_fluent_emoji.py /path/to/fluentui-emoji --style 3d

Other ``--style`` values: ``color``, ``flat``, ``high_contrast``.
